title: North Esports is looking for D+ Mid and Top Laners!!

embed.description: North Esports is very proud to present our very first RECRUITMENT CHALLENGE! Thankyou all for the support you have given us since we launched 3 days ago and we look forward to the response!

body:
Want to be a part of Australia's newest Esports team? You've come to the right place. North Esports is looking for Diamond + Mid and Top Laners to join our time in quest for the OPL in Season 6. If you fit these roles head to the video and apply through Twitter! Our twitter is www.twitter.com/northesportsne 

GAME ON

North Decos - Manager of North Esports
